    </a>
    <a href="/fallback-order" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-item-secondary">
        <strong>Fallback Order:</strong> <code>SharedModels.Order</code> (no
        <code>[ValidatableType]</code>) — same <code>IAsyncValidatableObject</code> via runtime Validator
    </a>
</div>

<h4>Comparison</h4>
<div class="list-group mb-3">
    <a href="/comparison" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-item-success">
        <strong>Side-by-Side:</strong> MEV <code>MevUserRegistration</code> vs Fallback
